Wilhelm, Kate. WHERE LATE THE SWEET BIRDS SANG. New York, Evanston, San Francisco, London: Harper & Row, Publishers, [1976]. Octavo, cloth-backed boards. First edition. Winner of the 1977 Hugo award for best novel. Anatomy of Wonder (2004) II-1248. Survey of Science Fiction Literature V, pp. 2469-73. A fine copy in fine dust jacket with touch of shelf wear to spine ends, several tiny rubbed spots on the front panel, and tiny closed tear to upper right corner. (#135665).

Price: $750.00
